{"tid":2072973,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"成日叫人躝躝躝，咁撚叻自己落場教落場踢","createTime":"2020-06-21T04:06:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-21T15:17:08.000Z","uid":108894,"like":8,"dislike":27,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"c0e8aad957e01be8bb21f7c597741d5a4c8a2e2b","tid":2072973,"uid":108894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T04:06:43.000Z","msg":"而家D連登車迷好難服侍<br />\n自己愛隊衰一兩場就叫林伯躝<br />\n但林伯又唔係教得好差<br />\n19/20夏季禁買人情況下教到咁已經好唔錯<br />\n要場場贏基本上只能夠fifa發生<br />\nAbraham又教得好<br />\n買Werner Ziyech都證明佢有決心砌隊頂級球隊<br />\n一季半季就話人係垃圾，我真係唔識睇波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n至少睇三季先判定林伯嘅能力啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過Zouma就真係要躝，傷完之後唔夠班，然後買過新中堅"},{"pid":"49cacfd8eff56d3bb8f104fd0acb6a862d047ca3","tid":2072973,"uid":318069,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T04:07:42.000Z","msg":"ching車迷黎咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"355fb7c8bb6decf2b362ea2c49dc047d6ea237c7","tid":2072973,"uid":108894,"like":0,"dislike":9,"score":-9,"quote":{"pid":"49cacfd8eff56d3bb8f104fd0acb6a862d047ca3","tid":2072973,"uid":318069,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T04:07:42.000Z","msg":"ching車迷黎咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T04:10:31.000Z","msg":"係<br />\n而且係林伯迷<br />\n佢仲踢緊波時日日J<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e767da5362badd7147714cfd21c89899368267f1","tid":2072973,"uid":32347,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T04:14:02.000Z","msg":"做咩摩一同摩二時期都唔睇三季呀咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eae8305b0d23991cabde19d143e0606980bd548d","tid":2072973,"uid":2169,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T04:14:41.000Z","msg":"個個黎都叫躝架啦"},{"pid":"ac884090d04b72f46304c8f43523e97d32f9bb4d","tid":2072973,"uid":3446